    "summary": "\u201cI want to leave the world in a lot better shape than I found it.\u201d\n\nRestorative | Futuristic | Strategic | Belief | Responsibility - These top 5 signature themes, according to Clifton\u2019s StrengthFinder by Gallup, define who I am at a personal and professional level.\n\nI am a results-driven Program Manager and Business Innovator with over 11 years of experience in delivering technology solutions and strategic initiatives for global organizations. Skilled at navigating complex challenges, I focus on driving continuous improvement, risk control, stakeholder engagement, and change management. My passion lies in driving growth and unlocking business value through innovative solutions, excellent communication, and cross-functional collaboration.\n\nMy key strengths include:\n\u2022 Diverse international experience across The Netherlands, Sweden, Germany, Thailand, India, and the USA\n\u2022 Extensive expertise in Service Delivery Management, Automation & Innovation, Project Management, Change Management, Digital Transformation Leadership, and Business Development & Pre-Sales\n\u2022 Proficient in Agile, DevOps, Design Thinking, Blockchain, and Artificial Intelligence\n\u2022 PMP\u00ae Certified Project Management Professional, Certified SAFe\u00ae 5 Agilist, Certified Scrum Master, Azure (AZ-900) certified, and multiple IBM Badges\n\u2022 Successful track record of cost savings, FTE reductions, and driving profitability for clients\n\u2022 Proven ability to lead, motivate, and manage diverse teams in cross-cultural environments\n\nThroughout my career, I have consistently delivered results, transforming projects and achieving significant cost savings, FTE reductions, and profitability improvements. My dedication to innovation and technology adoption has helped me excel in various roles across Project Management, Management Consulting, and Software Development.\n\nAs a goal-oriented leader with experience in strategic planning, budgeting, and resource allocation, I am committed to creating a positive impact on organizations through my technical expertise, strategic thinking, and passion for driving business value. With a focus on continuous improvement, I am always eager to explore new opportunities and take on greater responsibilities.\n\nMy commitment to leaving the world in a better shape extends beyond my professional life. I strive to contribute to social and environmental causes, aiming to create a lasting, positive impact on the world around me.\n\n\ud83d\udce9 Feel free to reach out at sudhsriv.de@gmail.com",
